[23:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this family consists of two different models. There\'s a pro variant which is 397 billion parameters. This is a mixture of experts models. So think of it as like a team of AIs working together. And when you use it, only 17'

[24:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'billion parameters are active. So this is fairly efficient. And then they also have a mini model. This is a lot smaller at 35 billion parameters and only 3 billion parameters are active when you use it. The awesome thing is this is out'

